I’m also reading that

“By default, the {{<thead>}} element and its contents do not receive keyboard focus unless they contain focusable elements with explicit {{tabindex}} values.”

I tried some javascript to set tabindex=0 on all of the thead’s and elements but that didn’t change anything. Not sure what this is missing. I think this needs to be more targeted but I figured something might happen. 

{noformat}  // Get all thead elements on the page
